                <h1 class="article-title">Trump’s Iranian Revolutionary Guard policy endangers the Middle East</h1>
                <div class="desktopRow">
                    <div id="d1">
                        <ul class="author">
                                                                                                                                                                                    <li class="author-shortcut author-pic">
                                                <a href="/author/giorgio.cafiero">
